{"pattern": {"comments_count":0,"created_at":"2026/07/15 12:15:44 -0400","currency":null,"difficulty_average":0,"difficulty_count":null,"downloadable":true,"favorites_count":25,"free":true,"gauge":null,"gauge_divisor":4,"gauge_pattern":"5\" approx","gauge_repeats":null,"generally_available":"2026/07/15 12:15:44 -0400","has_uk_terminology":null,"has_us_terminology":true,"id":7542093,"name":"The Web of Lies Square","pdf_url":"","permalink":"the-web-of-lies-square","price":null,"projects_count":1,"published":"2026/07/01","queued_projects_count":1,"rating_average":0,"rating_count":null,"row_gauge":null,"updated_at":"2026/07/15 23:03:52 -0400","url":"","yardage":null,"yardage_max":null,"yarn_list_type":2,"personal_attributes":null,"sizes_available":"","product_id":1086373,"unlisted_product_ids":null,"currency_symbol":null,"ravelry_download":true,"download_location":{"type":"ravelry","free":true,"url":"http://www.ravelry.com/dls/115683/1086373"},"pdf_in_library":false,"volumes_in_library":null,"gauge_description":"5\" approx","yarn_weight_description":"DK (11 wpi)","yardage_description":" yards","pattern_needle_sizes":[{"id":7,"us":"7.0","metric":4.5,"us_steel":null,"crochet":true,"knitting":false,"hook":null,"name":"4.5 mm","pretty_metric":"4.5"}],"notes_html":"\n<p>The Web of Lies Square <br />Welcome to square seven of The Great Granny Adventures CAL.</p>\n\n<p>Every mystery reaches a point where the clues no longer fit together quite so neatly.</p>\n\n<p>The Web of Lies Square was inspired by the tangled threads of a detective story …where every path seems to lead somewhere different, and every answer uncovers another question. Its openwork design creates a web-like motif that grows outwards from the centre, making it an enjoyable square to stitch and a beautiful addition to your growing collection.</p>\n\n<p>This PDF includes full written instructions in US crochet terms, and if you prefer to follow along visually, you’ll also find a free step-by-step YouTube tutorial.The Great Granny Adventures CAL features ten original granny squares, released one each month, before coming together in a collection of free final projects revealed in November.</p>\n\n<p>If you make your own Web of Lies Square, I’d love to see it! Share your photos on Instagram or TikTok tagging me @yarnivoremakes.</p>\n\n<p>The lies began to unravel ✨</p>\n","notes":"The Web of Lies Square\r\nWelcome to square seven of The Great Granny Adventures CAL.\r\n\r\nEvery mystery reaches a point where the clues no longer fit together quite so neatly.\r\n\r\nThe Web of Lies Square was inspired by the tangled threads of a detective story ...where every path seems to lead somewhere different, and every answer uncovers another question. Its openwork design creates a web-like motif that grows outwards from the centre, making it an enjoyable square to stitch and a beautiful addition to your growing collection.\r\n\r\nThis PDF includes full written instructions in US crochet terms, and if you prefer to follow along visually, you'll also find a free step-by-step YouTube tutorial.The Great Granny Adventures CAL features ten original granny squares, released one each month, before coming together in a collection of free final projects revealed in November.\r\n\r\nIf you make your own Web of Lies Square, I'd love to see it! Share your photos on Instagram or TikTok tagging me @yarnivoremakes.\r\n\r\nThe lies began to unravel ✨","languages":[{"code":"en","id":1,"name":"English","permalink":"en","short_name":"English","universal":false}],"packs":[{"id":142607206,"primary_pack_id":null,"project_id":null,"skeins":null,"stash_id":null,"total_grams":null,"total_meters":null,"total_ounces":null,"total_yards":null,"yarn_id":220426,"yarn_name":"Yarnsmiths (UK) Create DK","yarn_weight":{"crochet_gauge":null,"id":11,"knit_gauge":"22","max_gauge":null,"min_gauge":null,"name":"DK","ply":"8","wpi":"11"},"colorway":null,"shop_name":null,"yarn":{"permalink":"yarnsmiths-create-dk","id":220426,"nam